            <h3 data-uuid="c1b6825b68e54949a609138e8bd2c766">Part 2: Write an Explanatory Essay</h3>
            <h6 data-uuid="b93132ef809d43d689fce096dbe7d3c6">Historical Context</h6>
            <p data-uuid="18b1036da8c44381b75c152f3a1fbdec">Through an assortment of protests and legal battles, the African
                American civil rights movement made great strides in the 1950s and 1960s. Their
                successes spurred other groups to fight for their rights as well, altering the
                way the nation and its laws viewed a personâ€™s race, ethnicity, sex, and
                disability.</p>
            <h6 data-uuid="086fe4e3f14b464ba7c0a830e2ce10d6">Task</h6>
            <p data-uuid="b117786cd33c4353b95083c4b2be3f6a">Civil rights groups used a variety of methods to achieve their goals.
                What methods did they use? Were some more successful than others? Why? Write an
                explanatory essay to answer these questions.</p>
        </section>
        <p data-uuid="9e6df060727042a8a4c2fa8eeaf2bcb3">Complete the following steps as you plan and compose your essay.</p>
        <ol data-uuid="04c556c6a8d9446dadb87e7002e5f7ea">
            <li data-uuid="4d47dbc73a824207bc98473b44eda1ff">Review your notes and sources before you start writing.</li>
            <li data-uuid="0b8b81c3693c4b15a01a42313b383248">Use at least <i>two</i> of the sources in Part 1, and develop the topic with relevant, well-chosen text or visual evidence from the documents.</li>
            <li data-uuid="b4b5c27d18e8493e9a6729c976e5474f">Cite specific text evidence from each of the sources in your response.</li>
            <li data-uuid="52eed1c856234a4385861a19ea8b0ac0">Plan your essay so that it includes an introduction, several body paragraphs, and a concluding paragraph.</li>
            <li data-uuid="e1cfc1e578af43569e804be9e3e7cedc">Establish a formal tone and use transitions to improve the flow of your writing, connect ideas, and clarify meaning.</li>
            <li data-uuid="38919e1788224eacbe94053b13b703db">Organize your essay in a clear way that focuses on the topic and supports it with well-chosen facts, details, and examples.</li>
            <li data-uuid="1eca5e72829c4ded9a7a1cdb7fa143e9">Write a conclusion that sums up your ideas and supports the information you present.</li>
        </ol>
